{"tid":1154598,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山神知衰ig道歉 澄清不會離開曼聯 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2019-05-14T11:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T12:00:46.000Z","uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80f8bbb774a8ab3391da460b26d92af20a43daf9","tid":1154598,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"[隱藏]<br />\n紅魔陣中最高薪的山齊士，加盟一年半碌碌無為，煞科戰也因傷缺陣，不過似乎他較為着緊球會，並在ig向球迷道歉：「這是艱難一季，球迷應該得到一個道歉，他們無論何時何地都一直支持我們，我個人亦因各種傷患而踢不出水準。我肯定有一天，曼聯會回到費格遜領軍時代的輝煌。』<br />\n不過，山神亦指傳媒一切揣測都是虛假，似乎是表示自己無意離隊，對一眾已經徹底對山神失望的曼聯球迷而言，就未必是好消息。早前有傳聞指，曼聯已決定放棄山神，並願意支持其35萬鎊周薪的一半，務求有球會肯借走這位智利國腳。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2F&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ35V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=8b41fa5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2F&h=6cc55245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/</a> ... 2049&amp;a=59596717<br />\n<br />\n呢件報導2個重點，第一，踢成咁，仲有邊隊球隊仲肯比35萬磅週薪請你, 梗係唔走；第二，你唔走跟本係其他球隊喜訊！<img src=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/lol.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Flol.gif&h=6535e08c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27c809a81b40312b2b96852058cb0fb83a6a4c97","tid":1154598,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}